shortDescription.en-US: Das Team von Ottobock ist technisch und sprachlich breit aufgestellt.

altText.en-US: Das Team von Ottobock ist technisch und sprachlich breit aufgestellt.

shortDescription.en-US: 1988 fiel in Seoul der Startschuss fr unsere Partnerschaft mit den Paralympics. Seitdem ist Ottobock bei allen Paralympischen Sommer- und Winterspielen dabei und ebnet den AthletInnen den Weg fr einen sportlich-fairen Wettkampf.

People swimming with Aqualine
John with Running prosthesis taking a run on the beach.
Below-knee prosthesis with

altText.en-US: People swimming with Aqualine John with Running prosthesis taking a run on the beach. Below-knee prosthesis with: Harmon

headline.en-US: We help people maintain or regain their freedom of movement.

shortDescription.en-US: Our partnership with the Paralympics started in Seoul in 1988. Ottobock has been at every Summer and Winter Paralympic Games ever since, paving the way for good sportsmanship between the athletes.

altText.en-US: PARALYMPIC GAMES Passion for Paralympics Our partnership with the Paralympics started in Seoul in 1988. Ottobock has been at every Summer and Winter Paralympic Games ever since, paving the way for good sportsmanship between the athletes.
